          Apache-2.0. opened <a href="https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/pull/44074">PR #44074</a> in vLLM
          (pluggable sleep-mode backend), following participation in
          <a href="https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/issues/34303">RFC #34303</a>. sole-author paper on arXiv:
          <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.15621">"Re-feeding Is Not Replaying"</a> (June 2026).
        </p>
